    <p class="pg-sub">An evidence-based review of every reported creatine side effect in women — from the legitimate (mild GI discomfort) to the persistent myths (bulky muscles, hair loss, hormonal disruption). Sourced from 500+ peer-reviewed studies and 5-year safety data in female participants.</p>
    <div class="pg-meta">
      <span>Updated April 2026</span>
      <span>500+ Studies Reviewed</span>
      <span>Registered Dietitian Authored</span>
    </div>
  </section>

